{"tid":1354954,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣】何妖滑倒了","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:11:44.000Z","uid":28970,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5954a19589e0f6451f3e78452a8b72eb37d55d35","tid":1354954,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:41:25.000Z","msg":"唔關示威者事<br />\n係圍村佬收唔到尾數 走去搞人祖墳<br />\n<br />\n譴責白衫暴力<br />\n屌!<br />\n攪人個墳呢D 行為，一睇就知係圍村果班友做<br />\n<br />\n你知道嗎，何妖拖欠721晚黑社會尾數，導致家墳被破壞。 認同請分享<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又喺茶餐廳聽到<br />\n話鄉事大佬唔滿意何妖搞到件事收唔到科<br />\n所以派人去搞佢老母個墳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1TUffPK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1TUffPK.png&h=112cde7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmRpTBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmRpTBr.png&h=6ed2125d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrFBKH8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrFBKH8.png&h=e1e491b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"390972df7e56ea226e24537a33e6e9ae116685dc","tid":1354954,"uid":28970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:43:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話半打人守墳依加骨都差啲比人起埋啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"7f977c0b0c90e5ee550873c85ce26670ad1fdea0","tid":1354954,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"仲有升天南條住院費未找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2a5ad073f21a4dd58cc6bc6603c067f2301ae3","tid":1354954,"uid":141183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:47:28.000Z","msg":"我都聽到係咁 班白衫人 仲話係後面噴官黑勾結 就可以屈落黃絲到 其實明眼人一睇就知係白衫收唔夠錢做 邊個會咁蠢個黃絲敢咁做"},{"pid":"b8d7623f3b2640c1f597d6be739b1469fba9d271","tid":1354954,"uid":28970,"li